<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>BAWIPA CU A THA</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Zeizong te, sertu, Bawipa a, tha a tha
 Mi vialte, ca zongah, a tha e,
 Thleidannak, umlo, kan sining, tawk cio in
 A kan dawt, Bawipa cu a tha a tha.

[C1]
   Miphun kip nih, Cung Pathian cu
   Sangah hlorh uh, thangthatnak, Amah co seh,
   Kan taksa herhmi, Ni tlang le zilthli thiang
   Man loin, a kan petu, Bawipa a si.

[V2]
 A sermi, lak ah, a kut chuak, Minung hi
 Huham ngei, phun dangin, a kan ser
 Ni fatin, tein, a kan ven, tuu bangin
 Bawipa cu, kan caah, a tha a tha.</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
</song>